data.description: Great opportunity to own this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single family home that spans 1,188 square feet and is situated in a great neighborhood. Nice floor plan to include formal living area with big front window, kitchen opens to dining area/family room with fireplace. All good-sized bedrooms provide comfort ands space! Screened-in porch overlooks fenced-in, private backyard. Attached 1 car garage and plenty of parking! Nestled on .32 acres, there is plenty of outdoor space! This home has a lot to offer, come check it out today!
